{"tid":2267384,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"張竹君在高等法院出庭作供 有市民要求與她自拍","createTime":"2020-11-02T04:47:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-02T11:26:53.000Z","uid":240362,"like":38,"dislike":184,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"4eee5a8db74d2badcd4ec28d9d9df0755e61b57c","tid":2267384,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T04:47:11.000Z","msg":"2012年DR醫學美容中心發生致命事故，三位女顧客接受「CIK療程」後感染細菌，造成一死兩傷殘。為事主注射血液製品的女西醫被控嚴重疏忽誤殺罪，案件今在高等法院續審。控方傳召衞生署衞生防護中心顧問醫生張竹君出庭，透露衞生署當日得悉有兩名病人疑感染細菌，導致敗血性休克等情況，署方即晚展開調查，認為感染源頭為DR位於大埔科學園的血液培植中心。張醫生完成作供乘電梯離開法庭期間，有市民興奮地要求與她自拍，並向張醫生表示「加油」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201102/3VTS4QT53FDXHIOJH5CZTGMW5U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201102%2F3VTS4QT53FDXHIOJH5CZTGMW5U%2F&d=Vpe8FAkBT2vLq%2FWrgjLHxZktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=7893547f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201102%2F3VTS4QT53FDXHIOJH5CZTGMW5U%2F&h=a7fb0401\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201102/3VTS4QT53FDXHIOJH5CZTGMW5U/</a>"},{"pid":"ea2155b405536a53e54bbab7d0ee79e19281ff80","tid":2267384,"uid":51469,"like":55,"dislike":1,"score":54,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T04:47:53.000Z","msg":"好彩今日冇記者會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f902989c34e1bbec88fd4bd9f0bb9041d7a2036b","tid":2267384,"uid":135867,"like":339,"dislike":30,"score":309,"citedBy":14,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T04:52:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔明點解受歡迎<br />\n同新聞報道員有咩分別<br />\n有連登仔出post話佢老公有病佢要兩邊走好慘我先奇怪<br />\n佢都係官來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咪唔記得左啲咩"},{"pid":"5aa6a6847fada9f314886298220668c7365672d6","tid":2267384,"uid":11291,"like":40,"dislike":3,"score":37,"quote":{"pid":"f902989c34e1bbec88fd4bd9f0bb9041d7a2036b","tid":2267384,"uid":135867,